hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Could I have a statement, please? baby fever ibuprofen or tylenol Number one, globalization.  Right?  Capital, companies, they can move businesses and– and jobs– anywhere they want.  And so they’re lookin’ for the lowest wages.  That squeezes workers here in the United States, even if corporations are profitable.  Technology.  If you go to– a lot of companies now, they’ve eliminated entire occupations because they’re now robotized.  We don’t have travel agents.  We don’t have bank tellers.
